		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">This research is in three parts.1. The first part is to make further headway with the method of amalgamations, in particular to pairs of mututally orthogonal latin squares (Graeco-Latin squares) and to Kirkman triple systems.2. The second part is to study recent work by Glebsky and Gordon on approximations to locally compact groups with a view to answering some obvious questions about them.3. The third part is to try to solve some recent problems arising in the study of graph-theoretical analogues of the Erdos-Ko-Rado theorem.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
